727382f-a.text:
Merrick Bouleverd, south side, between 223rd and 224th Streets,viewing east from the former and showing an old farmhorse. The farmhouse apoears on Walverton's 1891 map (plate 28), but its ownership is not indicated. It was situated between the property of A. H. Higbie and J. Compton.
March 9, 1927
P. L. Sperr
